
#SingleInstance, Force

^SPACE::

KeyWait, LButton
Hotkey, *LButton,% NoLB?"On":("Return",NoLB := True)

Sleep, 10000 	 ; Mouse L-Click resumes after 10 seconds.

Hotkey, *LButton, Off
Return:
Return

;  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  

RETURN

^HOME:: 
    Reload

^Esc::
    ExitApp
;  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  ̶  
